&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Given:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;The successive discount are&amp;nbsp;20% and 15%.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Formula used:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;Successive discount = X + Y - (XY)/100&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;Where,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;X = First discount&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;Y = Second discount&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Calculation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;Successive discount =&amp;nbsp;X + Y - (XY)/100&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;X = 20%, Y = 15%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 20&amp;nbsp;+ 15&amp;nbsp;- 300/100&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 32%&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important; font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; The single equivalent discount is 32%.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;P&amp;#39;s salary is 60% of Q&amp;#39;s salary which is 50% of R&amp;#39;s salary.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;P&amp;#39;s Salary = 60% of Q&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;= 60% of (50% of R)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;= (60/100)[(50/100)*100]&amp;nbsp;% of R&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;= 30% of R&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; P&amp;#39;s salary is 30% of R&amp;#39;s salary.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/alternate-methord-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Alternate Method&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let Q salary be&amp;nbsp;100&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;P salary =&amp;nbsp;60&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;R salary = 200&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;P salary = 60/200&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 100 = 30% of R salary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ratio of the number of boys to that of girls in a school is 11 ∶ 15.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;the number of boys and girls in a school be 11a and 15a.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 15a - 11a = 200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 4a = 200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; a = 50&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 11a &amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;50 &amp;times; 11 = 550&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The number of boys in that school is 550.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Given,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Average age of group of 75 people is = 75&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Formula : &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Average = Sum of all observations/Total number of all observations&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Calculation : &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Sum of age of group of 75 people = 75 &amp;times; 75 = 5625&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;If a person of age 90 left and a person of age 15 joined the group, then new sum of age of 75 people = 5625 &amp;ndash; 90 + 15 = 5550&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; New average age of 75 people = 5550/75 = 74&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shortcut Trick:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Correct Average = Average + difference/Total number&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; New average age of 75 people = 75 &amp;ndash; (90 + 15)/75 = 75 &amp;ndash; 1 = 74&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Principal (P)&amp;nbsp;= 12,500&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Amount (A): 15,500&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Time (t) = 4 year&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(S.I. = \frac{P \times R \times t}{100}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;S.I = Amount - Principal&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Calculation:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; S.I. = 15,500 - 12,500&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;S.I. = 3,000&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(3,000 = \frac{12,500 \times R \times 4}{100}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(R = \frac{3000 \times 100}{12,500 \times 4}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; R = 6%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; correct answer is 6%&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
